overview: Luna, 19, leaves her family and friends behind  to ​join one of the world’s best Competition Dance ​Schools.This is her big chance to compete in the biggest ​dance competition in the country; if she wins, ​she’ll be offered jobs, events, and galas, all at ​high-paying prices. However, things don’t go as ​planned when she doesn’t get on the top team.
title: Dance Squad
